videos.description: Kenny Williams gets free in transition and eludes NC State defenders with a sweet Eurostep finish.
videos.headline: Williams goes coast-to-coast for nice Eurostep finish

videos.description: Braxton Beverly cuts into North Carolina's lead as he drains two back-to-back 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Beverly's back-to-back 3s ignite NC State run

videos.description: NC State's DJ Funderburk rises for a nasty two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Funderburk throws down monster, two-handed slam

videos.description: NC State's Markell Johnson flies through the air and slams home a sick one-handed dunk and follows it up with a nice steal for an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: Johnson skies for nasty one-handed slam

videos.description: Markell Johnson dazzles with a sweet bounce pass to Torin Dorn who finishes with a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Johnson's sweet bounce pass leads to Dorn slam

videos.description: Leaky Black seals the win for UNC as he slips past NC State defenders for a wide-open two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Black seals the game with two-handed jam
